imdb.plot outline: The story goes on in the South East in 1997 when the terrorist incidents increased. While the soldiers are being martyred, the people of the region also suffer serious damage from terrorism. People are classified as pro-terrorist and pro-state. When a child living in the region travels to the Military Academy, the remaining family members are brutally murdered by terrorists.
